## ğŸ“ Description

System Severity is a Python-based tool designed to help you manage and understand the severity of issues within your systems. It provides a comprehensive approach through its API, allowing for seamless integration with existing infrastructure. A robust database backend ensures reliable storage and retrieval of severity data. Thorough testing guarantees stability and accuracy, while the command-line interface (CLI) offers a convenient way to interact with the system directly. Whether you need to automate severity assessments or gain deeper insights into your system's health, System Severity offers a versatile and dependable solution.

   - Unix/MacOS: `source venv/bin/activate`
